'''[[whoopee]] [[cushion]]''' (''plural'' '''whoopee cushions''')

#An inflatable bag containing a [[valve]] at its neck that retains the air in the bag until pressure is put on it (usually by someone unintentionally sitting on it after it has been placed on a chair by someone else as a [[practical joke]]), when the air is [[expel]]led with a sound similar to that of someone [[break wind|breaking wind]].